data.description: Relax in the wilderness. Get away from it all and enjoy the peace and quiet. This home sits on a stem wall, has an open floor plan, and a wood burning stove to keep you warm in the winter. Keep your pets contained in the fenced backyard. The oversized detached garage has electrical and plenty of opportunity to make into your dream shop. The house sits off of the road away from passing cars. If you're ready to get away from the hustle and bustle of the city this is the home for you.
